io.odysz.semantics

Interface IResults


  • public interface IResults
    Resultset interface, for separating semantic.DA and semantic.transact. This interface is somehow like the ResultSet, but the result set is not connection based. All results can be used without worrying about db connect and updating - no updating supported. Currently IResults has only one implementation class, the semantic.DA/io.odysz.module.rs.SResultset.
    Author:
    odys-z@github.com
